ोधः॥३९॥\r\n\r\n<b>PYS 2.39: Aparigraha sthairye janma kathānta sambodhah</b>\r\n\r\n<i>knowledge of past and future lives unfolds as one is freed from greed for possessions</i>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Yama', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-10 20:44:54', '2013-11-10 20:44:54', '', 48, 'http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/?p=49', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
