 in yoga. All basic yoga postures will be taught including shoulder stand and relaxation.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Friday - Restorative class</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n1 - 2pm\r\n\r\nThis is a slower pace class suitable for all levels. Poses will be practised supported to help the body recover at the end of the week. This type of practice helps us prolong the timing in the poses and deepen the experience. More attention is given to the breath and basic breathing exercises will be taught regularly in this class.\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Classes are suitable for all, no previous yoga experience needed!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 24px;">Prices from January<a href="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/49for10circle.png"><img class="alignright  wp-image-172" style="margin: 20px 50px;" title="£49 for 10 classes" alt="49for10circle" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/49for10circle-300x300.png" width="180" height="180" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nLunchtime Classes - 1 hour\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>New Student Offer!</em></span>\r\n10-class Yogacard - £49 for 6 weeks\r\n\r\n10-class Yogacard - £70 for 12 weeks\r\n\r\nDrop-in - £8\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEvening classes - 1.5 hours\r\n\r\n10-class Yogacard - £90 for 12 weeks\r\nDrop-in - £10\r\n\r\nView full Yoga Loft Timetable here!\r\n\r\nYogaloft is a fully equipped studio at Queen Square, Bristol\r\n\r\n<img class=" wp-image-181 alignleft" style="margin-right: 20px; margin-left: 20px;" title="Osteopaths" alt="Osteopaths Logo" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Osteopaths-Logo.png" width="38" height="24" />Osteopaths, 57 Queen Charlotte Street, Bristol BS1 4HQ\r\n<iframe src="https://maps.google.co.uk/maps?ie=UTF8&amp;cid=3098133523227739122&amp;gl=GB&amp;hl=en&amp;t=m&amp;ll=51.451533,-2.594211&amp;spn=0.05,0.05&amp;z=16&amp;&amp;iwloc=near&amp;output=embed" height="350" 