(218, 1, '2013-12-07 11:55:56', '2013-12-07 11:55:56', '<h3><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-250" style="margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" alt="BCY-Logo" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/BCY-Logo.jpg" width="124" height="85" />General Class</h3>\r\n<address><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong>Mondays 9.30am - 11am</strong></span></address><strong>Starting 6th January 2014\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Bristol City Yoga</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.bristolcityyoga.co.uk">www.bristolcityyoga.co.uk </a>\r\n<em>16 Backfields Lane, Bristol, BS2 8QW</em>\r\n\r\nThis class is open to all levels.\r\n\r\nIt is a dynamic and well rounded class.  We also look at all the basic principals to assure your practice foundation is grounded through alignment and understanding of the base of the posture. All inverted poses are taught according to the level of students.\r\n\r\nRelaxation and breath awareness techniques are taught regularly.\r\n\r\nA perfect way to start your week!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>', 'Bristol City Yoga', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bristol-city-yoga', '', '', '2013-12-22 09:16:22', '2013-12-22 09:16:22', '', 37, 'http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/?page_id=218', 5, 'page', '', 0),
