(237, 1, '2013-12-07 12:44:07', '2013-12-07 12:44:07', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-201" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;" title="Yoga Loft Bristol" alt="YogaLoftLogoAddress" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/YogaLoftLogoAddress-e1386005646620.png" width="600" height="152" />\r\n<strong>Four new lunchtime classes at Yoga Loft Bristol from 6th January 2014!</strong>\r\n<h4>Monday - Foundation</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nStep by step introduction to the basic yoga postures. Perfect for yoga novices or those who like to brush up on yoga foundation in this progressively structured class.\r\n<h4>Wednesday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a class for all levels from beginners to improvers. We will be focusing on different postures every week and basic breathing techniques will also be taught.\r\n<h4>Thursday - Beginners</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nDynamic class suitable for those with little or no experience in yoga. All basic yoga postures will be taught including shoulder stand and relaxation.\r\n<h4>Friday - Restorative</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a slower pace class suitable for all levels. Poses will be practised supported to help the body recover at the end of the week. This type of practice helps us prolong the timing in the poses and deepen the experience. More attention is given to the breath and basic breathing exercises will be taught regularly in this class.\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Classes are suitable for all, no previous yoga experience needed!</span>\r\n<h1><span style="font-size: 24px;">Prices from January</span></h1>\r\n<h4>1 hour Lunchtime Class</h4>\r\n<h1><span style="font-size: 24px;"><img class="alignright  wp-image-172" style="margin: 10px;" title="£49 for 10 classes" alt="£49 for 10 Classes" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/49for10circle-300x300.png" width="180" height="180" /></span></