(301, 1, '2014-01-10 19:16:43', '2014-01-10 19:16:43', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-201" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;" title="Yoga Loft Bristol" alt="YogaLoftLogoAddress" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/YogaLoftLogoAddress-e1386005646620.png" width="600" height="152" /><span style="font-size: 28px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">New!!</span> Lunchtime Yoga Classes at Yoga Loft, Bristol </span>\r\n\r\nI''m teaching 4 new lunchtime classes at Yogaloft: Mo, We, Thu &amp; Fri 1 - 2pm\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="font-family: Bitter, Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3;">Monday - Beginners </span></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nStep by step introduction to the basic yoga postures. Perfect for yoga novices or those who like to brush up on yoga foundation in this progressively structured class. All standing poses will be practiced regularly and you will learn to do Shoulder Stand and variation here. All other groups of poses will be also introduced.\r\n<h4>Wednesday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a class for all levels from beginners to improvers. We will be focusing on different postures every week and basic breathing techniques will also be taught.\r\n<h4>Thursday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nDynamic class suitable for all. All basic yoga postures will be taught including shoulder stand and relaxation.\r\n<h4>Friday - Restorative</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a slower pace class suitable for all levels. Poses will be practised supported to help the body recover at the end of the week. This type of practice helps us prolong the timing in the poses and deepen the experience. More attention is given to the breath and basic breathing exercises will be taught regularly in this class.\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Classes are suitable for all, no previous yoga experience needed!</span>\r\n\r\nDrop-in, no need to book!\r\n<h1><span style="font-size: 24px;">Prices: </span></h1>\r\n<h4>1 hour Lunchtime Class</h4>\r\n<h1><span style="font-size: 24px;"><img class="alignright  wp-image-172" style="margin: 10px;" title="£49 for 10 classes" alt="£49 for 10 Classes" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/49for10circle-300x300.png" width="180" height="180" /></span></h1>\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>*New Student Offer!</em></span>\r\n10-class Yogacard - £49 for 6 weeks\r\n\r\n10-class Yogacard - £70 for 12 weeks\r\n\r\nDrop-in - £8\r\n<h4>1.5 hour Evening classes</h4>\r\n10-class Yogacard - £90 for 12 weeks\r\nDrop-in - £10\r\n\r\n<a title="Coming Soon!">View full Yoga Loft Timetable here!</a>\r\n\r\nYoga Loft is a fully equipped studio at Queen Square, Bristol\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-181 alignnone" style="margin-right: 20px; margin-left: 20px;" title="Osteopaths" alt="Osteopaths Logo" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Osteopaths-Logo.png" width="38" height="24" />Osteopaths, 57 Queen Charlotte Street, Bristol BS1 4HQ\r\n<iframe src="https://maps.google.co.uk/maps?ie=UTF8&amp;cid=3098133523227739122&amp;gl=GB&amp;hl=en&amp;t=m&amp;ll=51.451533,-2.594211&amp;spn=0.05,0.05&amp;z=16&amp;&amp;iwloc=near&amp;output=embed" height="350" width="600" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>', 'Yoga Loft', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-10 19:16:43', '2014-01-10 19:16:43', '', 154, 'http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/posts/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
