(326, 1, '2014-01-12 20:20:43', '2014-01-12 20:20:43', '<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-201" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;" title="Yoga Loft Bristol" alt="YogaLoftLogoAddress" src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/YogaLoftLogoAddress-e1386005646620.png" width="600" height="152" /><span style="font-size: 28px;">Lunchtime Yoga Classes at Yoga Loft, Bristol </span>\r\n\r\nI''m teaching 4 new lunchtime classes at Yogaloft: every Mon, Wed, Thu &amp; Fri 1 - 2pm\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="font-family: Bitter, Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3;">Monday - Beginners </span></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nStep by step introduction to the basic yoga postures. Perfect for yoga novices or those who like to brush up on yoga foundation in this progressively structured class. All standing poses will be practiced regularly and you will learn to do Shoulder Stand and variation here. All other groups of poses will be also introduced.\r\n<h4>Wednesday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a class for all levels from beginners to improvers. We will be focusing on different postures every week and basic breathing techniques will also be taught.\r\n<h4>Thursday - General</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nDynamic class suitable for all. All basic yoga postures will be taught including shoulder stand and relaxation.\r\n<h4>Friday - Restorative</h4>\r\n<em>1 - 2pm</em>\r\nThis is a slower pace class suitable for all levels. Poses will be practised supported to help the body recover at the end of the week. This type of practice helps us prolong the timing in the poses and deepen the experience. More attention is given to the breath and basic breathing exercises will be taught regularly in this class.\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Classes are suitable for all, no previous yoga experience needed!</span>\r\n\r\nDrop-in, no need to book!\r\n<h1><span style="font-size: 24px;">Prices: </span></