(393, 1, '2015-05-30 09:38:42', '2015-05-30 09:38:42', '<h4><img src="http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shapeimage_41.png" alt="Stick figure Yoga" width="910" height="492" /></h4>\n<h3>General public classes</h3>\nI''m currently based in Ealing, West London.  I''m looking to start teaching general classes in this area soon.\n<h3><span style="font-family: Bitter, Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.3;">Private classes</span></h3>\nOne-to-one classes have the benefit of focusing directly on your specific needs and goals. It is a great way to get to know and understand your body whilst addressing your particular tendencies and weak areas. One-to-one is the traditional way of teaching which allows the student to practice exactly according to their personal needs under close guidance of an experienced teacher.\n\nFamily class or a small group class can also be arranged.\n\nThese classes can be offered at the comfort of your home and necessary equipment will need to be available.\n<h3>Corporate classes</h3>\nCorporate yoga classes are a fantastic way to boost the work morale and well being of employees. Yoga helps build strength, stamina, balance and flexibility, whilst creating a balanced mental state with strong sense of vitality and health.\n\nI offer lunchtime and evening classes on-site. Suitable space will need to be arranged to accommodate all the participants. Basic yoga equipment will also need to be provided.\n\n<strong>Private and corporate classes are priced at £60 for 1 hour class or £45 for 45 min class.</strong>\n\n<!--[subpage_peek]-->', 'Classes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '37-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-30 09:38:42', '2015-05-30 09:38:42', '', 37, 'http://localhost:8888/wpyogdiksha-nov2013/posts/37-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
